"{\"uid\": \"joe.co.uk-sport-andy-murray-confirms-paris-olympics-will-be-final-ever-tennis-tournament-449686\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Play the JOE Pub Quiz  Share  Published08:13 23 Jul 2024 BST  Updated08:36 23 Jul 2024 BST  Andy Murray has said this summer's Olympics will be his \\\"last ever tennis tournament.\\\"\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe's_Own_Editor\", \"score\": 0.9999999947799552, \"rank\": 5.220106091074871e-09, \"text\": \"JOE\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe's_Own_Editor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe's_Own_Editor\"}, {\"begin\": 57, \"end\": 60, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0404459369843184e-16, \"text\": \"BST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\"}, {\"begin\": 87, \"end\": 90, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0404459369843184e-16, \"text\": \"BST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\"}, {\"begin\": 92, \"end\": 103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1583497551165918e-49, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-old has travelled to Paris as part of Team GB to compete in the tennis, having won gold at both the 2012 and 2016 games.\", \"from\": 180, \"to\": 312, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 213, \"end\": 218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.549159990670186e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 230, \"end\": 237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.998651888767857, \"rank\": 0.0011240275674173558, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a post on X on Tuesday morning, he said representing Great Britain at the Olympics has given him \\\"the most memorable weeks\\\" of his career.\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 370, \"end\": 383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\", \"score\": 0.9920176672689288, \"rank\": 0.005215732532610655, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"Arrived in Paris for my last ever tennis tournament @Olympics.\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 478, \"end\": 483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.549159990670186e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Competing for [Great Britain] have been by far the most memorable weeks of my career and I am extremely proud to get do it one final time!\\\"\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One fan commented: \\\"Very best wishes for your final tournament.\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 736, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You will be sorely missed.\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have done the UK proud.\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 782, \"end\": 784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999999545253, \"rank\": 4.545482896611285e-11, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's to happiness and success in all the future brings.\\\"\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another said: \\\"You are such a wonderful tennis player and role model.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your dedication and especially your success (Grand Slams, Olympic gold) make you a true inspiration.\\\"\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 1023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A third wrote: \\\"I saw you play both singles and mixed doubles in London 2012.\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1090, \"end\": 1101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999414244501, \"rank\": 5.7501811608025214e-08, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the highlights of my life!\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Good luck for Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1151, \"end\": 1156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.549159990670186e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tennis at the Paris Olympics will take place on the clay of Roland Garros, and Murray is set to take part in the men's singles and doubles.\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1224, \"end\": 1237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999476923187428, \"rank\": 5.231039802217887e-05, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}, {\"begin\": 1243, \"end\": 1249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.297617009936797e-23, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For months now, Murray has said he does not plan to play much tennis after the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.297617009936797e-23, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, this is the first time he has officially confirmed that the games will be his final tournament.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this month, the Scot bidan emotional farewell to Wimbledonafter he lost in the first round of the men's doubles alongside his brother Jamie on Centre Court.\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1652, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Centre Court\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Centre_Court\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said in June that retiring after Wimbledon or the Olympics would be \\\"fitting\\\", given the 